oyees well we pay our highestperforming talent at the top of the market we offer an exceptional array of benefits and we are always searching for ways to take care of our employees and their families our best years are yet to come while we are fortunate to have enjoyed considerable success since our founding i believe our best years remain ahead of us tectonic shifts in our industry are fostering enormous opportunities for a sophisticated player like bluemountain – and the people who drive its success very truly yours andrew feldstein ceococio explore opportunities we love to work with talented people who embody our values and strive to make a lasting impact explore our current open positions below we look forward to hearing from you it infrastructure database engineer quantitative strategy  operations strategist finance fund controller senior fund accountant administrative services investment team executive assistant operations pnl analyst – london investing in our people benefitstrainingwomens initiativeevents we provide bestinclass benefits for all of our employees in a unique fun and collaborative work environment some of our benefits include excellent medical dental and vision plans for you and your family k retirement plan with annual company contribution a comprehensive wellness program stateoftheart office spaces commuter benefits program  fully paid parental leave  weekly catered breakfast series and fullystocked pantries specialty gifts for extraordinary contributors  generous paid time off  worklife balance and firmsponsored social events find out what being part of our family means for your family read more about our parental benefits or view our brochure we invest in our talent we offer our people opportunities for cultivating their knowledge and skills through training programs such as executive communication skills these programs expand the verbal and written range of even our most experienced communicators management training we train new and experie