dge fund manager it provides its services to pooled investment vehicles operating as private investment funds and institutional accounts typically operating as singleinvestor limited partnerships or foreign companies the firm manages separate clientfocused portfolios it invests in public equity fixed income and alternative investment markets across the globe for its alternative investments the firm invests in longshort credit longshort equity distressed and special situations clos assetbacked securities synthetic structured credit mortgages commercial real estate volatility convertibles and indexbond basis strategies it employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios bluemountain capital management llc was founded in  and is based in new york new york detailed description  park avenueth floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwbluemountaincapitalcom key executives for bluemountain capital management llc mr andrew todd feldstein jd ceo cochief investment officer and partner age  mr stephen miles siderow jd copresident and partner mr michael liberman chief operating officer partner and copresident mr derek s smith cochief investment officer and partner age  mr paul friedman jd general counsel chief administrative officer and partner compensation as of fiscal year  bluemountain capital management llc key developments bluemountain capital management appoints claudio macchetto as head of platform distribution jul   bluemountain capital management has appointed claudio macchetto as its head of platform distribution in his new role macchetto will be responsible for the marketing of bluemountains diversified alternative investment strategies to wealth management channels and private banking platforms as well as the management of retail distribution relationships globally the appointment is effective from july  prior to this appointment macchetto worked for paulson  co as its managing director he has also worked with citi